  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="Dear"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
               <l>I am not land or timber</l>
               <l>nor are you</l> 
               <l>ocean or celestial body,</l>
               <l>                       </l>
               <l>but rather we are</l>
               <l>the small animals</l>
               <l>we have always been.</l>
               <l>                 </l>
               <l>The land and the sea</l>
               <l>know each other</l>
               <l>at the threshold</l>
               <l>                 </l>
               <l>where they meet,</l>
               <l>as we know something</l>
               <l>of one another,</l>
               <l>                 </l>
               <l>having shown,</l>
               <l>at different times,</l>
               <l>some bit of flesh,</l>
               <l>                 </l>
               <l>some feeling.</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>We call the showing</l>
               <l>knowing instead of practice.</l>
               <l>We seem to say,</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>at different times,</l>
               <l>A feeling comes.</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>What is the metaphor</l>
               <l>for two animals</l>
               <l>sharing the same space?</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>Marriage?</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>We share a practice,</l>
               <l>you and I,</l>
               <l>a series of postures.</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>Here is how I</l>
               <l>become a tree</l>
               <l>[                            ]</l>
               <l>                  </l>
               <l>and you</l>
               <l>[                            ]</l>
               <l>a body in space.</l>
        <l>           Donika Kelly</l> 
               <note><ref target="#Dear"></ref></note>
               <!-- I just made this up here -->
             </lg>
